Package entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assessment
    Stores data about an assessment that a teacher would assign, for example: Name: Unit 4 Math Test Course: Math Weight: 4 Categories: Knowledge, Thinking
    AssessmentMark
    Stores information about a mark a student has, for example: Assessment: Unit 4 Math test Marks: Knowledge - 60%, Application - 80%
    Course
    Stores information about a course, including the name, a list of the assessments in that course, and the weights for each category.
    CourseAssociation
    Represents the connection between a Person object and a Course object.
    Credentials
    Stores a username, password pair that belongs to a Person object.
    Person
    Stores information about a person that is a member of a school.
    Student
    Stores information about a student.
    StudentCourseAssociation
    Stores information about a course enrollment that a student has
    Teacher
    Stores information about a teacher
    TeacherCourseAssociation
    Stores information about the connection between a teacher and a course they teach
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AssessmentCategory
    Categories that a mark can belong to: Knowledge Thinking Application Communication
